<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 13:17:20 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>埃里克·特朗普 (Eric Trump) 从陷入困境的金融科技公共领导层中消失</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-30/eric-trump-disappears-from-troubled-fintech-s-public-leadership</link><description>埃里克·特朗普(Eric Trump)已从拉斯维加斯一家小型公司的公共领导层中消失，这家公司与其家族的加密货币公司世界自由金融公司(World Liberty Financial Inc.)关系密切。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ii_JhJD6Ab_8/v2/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 11:46:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-30/eric-trump-disappears-from-troubled-fintech-s-public-leadership</guid></item><item><title>Tether 敦促 Jack Mallers 的“二十一”进行罢工和矿工交易</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-30/tether-proposes-mergers-involving-bitcoin-treasury-company</link><description>Tether 提议 Twenty One Capital 与加密货币交易和支出平台 Strike 以及比特币挖矿公司 Elektron Energy 合并，而此时 Twenty One Capital 投资比特币的主要业务已经失宠。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/itQPSikuECwc/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 00:47:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-30/tether-proposes-mergers-involving-bitcoin-treasury-company</guid></item><item><title>期权交易者以 80,000 美元围绕比特币搭建“电子围栏”</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-29/option-traders-build-electric-fence-around-bitcoin-at-80-000</link><description>比特币一直逼近8万美元，但仍难以突破。原因之一：期权市场中的一股隐藏力量正在对其产生不利影响。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ioEL9BrYJSPg/v2/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 Apr 2026 15:53:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-29/option-traders-build-electric-fence-around-bitcoin-at-80-000</guid></item><item><title>捷克央行行长表示比特币可能有助于增加储备</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-28/czech-central-banker-says-bitcoin-may-improve-reserve-portfolio</link><description>捷克共和国最高央行行长 Ales Michl 周二表示，将比特币添加到该银行的官方储备中可以改善投资组合的表现，最新评论表明该机构继续认真考虑多元化发展数字资产。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ik3kfo_1G8no/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 Apr 2026 20:10:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-28/czech-central-banker-says-bitcoin-may-improve-reserve-portfolio</guid></item><item><title>加密货币公司 MoonPay 押注 1 亿美元用于机构推动</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-29/crypto-firm-moonpay-bets-100-million-for-institutional-push</link><description>MoonPay Inc. 收购了以色列加密安全初创公司 Sodot，这是该加密支付公司计划推出一个专门致力于满足机构对数字资产需求的新部门的一部分。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ihaRJeExzYiA/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 Apr 2026 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-29/crypto-firm-moonpay-bets-100-million-for-institutional-push</guid></item><item><title>稳定币巨头 Tether 领投阿根廷加密货币应用程序</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-29/stablecoin-giant-tether-leads-investment-in-argentine-crypto-app</link><description>Tether 通过投资阿根廷加密平台 Belo 进一步进军拉丁美洲。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iQwyGymKEOJM/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 Apr 2026 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-29/stablecoin-giant-tether-leads-investment-in-argentine-crypto-app</guid></item><item><title>山姆·班克曼-弗里德重新审判的动议被美国法官驳回</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-28/sam-bankman-fried-s-motion-for-new-trial-rejected-by-us-judge</link><description>一名联邦法官驳回了 FTX 联合创始人 Sam Bankman-Fried 提出的自行动议，要求根据这位前加密货币之王声称的新证据进行新的审判。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iV5O8v7917bU/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 Apr 2026 21:23:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-28/sam-bankman-fried-s-motion-for-new-trial-rejected-by-us-judge</guid></item><item><title>最新 DeFi 黑客事件动摇信心，以太坊面临十字路口</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-04-28/ether-eth-faces-a-crossroad-as-defi-hacks-shake-confidence</link><description>第二大加密货币的价值越来越依赖于其上构建的一切的弹性。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i6Ftz9vspNJU/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 Apr 2026 21:00:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-04-28/ether-eth-faces-a-crossroad-as-defi-hacks-shake-confidence</guid></item><item><title>摩根大通任命前高盛高管领导区块链部门</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-28/jpmorgan-taps-former-goldman-executive-to-lead-blockchain-unit</link><description>摩根大通公司已任命前高盛集团高管 Oliver Harris 领导其区块链部门 Kinexys，该银行希望扩大使用加密基础技术构建的产品和服务的采用。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iSrOiB_ha8Co/v2/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 Apr 2026 16:00:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-28/jpmorgan-taps-former-goldman-executive-to-lead-blockchain-unit</guid></item><item><title>Polymarket 寻求 CFTC 批准将主要交易所带回美国</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-28/polymarket-seeks-cftc-blessing-to-bring-main-exchange-back-to-us</link><description>据知情人士透露，Polymarket 正在采取措施，试图将其主要交易所带回美国，通过允许美国人访问该平台，可能会为已经快速增长的行业带来动力。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/icGoU2A7ktAs/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 Apr 2026 15:03:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-28/polymarket-seeks-cftc-blessing-to-bring-main-exchange-back-to-us</guid></item><item><title>Novogratz 表示比特币重夺 10 万美元将很困难</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-28/novogratz-s-galaxy-digital-posts-loss-as-crypto-rout-lingers</link><description>亿万富翁 Michael Novogratz 表示，在当前的宏观经济环境下，以市场领头羊比特币交易价格再次超过 10 万美元来衡量，加密货币领域的广泛复苏可能会很困难。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iikdUX6WTmck/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 Apr 2026 12:20:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-28/novogratz-s-galaxy-digital-posts-loss-as-crypto-rout-lingers</guid></item></channel></rss>